OL,3,CMan dies in hospital week after attack
OL,5,FA man has died following an assault in
OL,6,Fthe Suffolk Road area of west Belfast
OL,7,Flast Friday.
OL,9,FCarl Holland, 30, was from the local
OL,10,Farea, police said.
OL,12,FThey said his attacker arrived in a
OL,13,Ftaxi, punched Mr Holland and then left
OL,14,Fin again in a taxi.
OL,16,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "We can
OL,17,Fconfirm that Carl Holland has sadly
OL,18,Fpassed away, and our thoughts are,
OL,19,Ffirst and foremost, with his family
OL,20,Fand friends at this extremely
OL,21,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
