PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781873290
OL,3,CMan dies in hospital week after attack
OL,5,F"Carl was the victim of an assault,
OL,6,Fwhich happened outside licensed
OL,7,Fpremises in the Suffolk Road area of
OL,8,Fthe city on the night of Friday June
OL,9,F12.
OL,11,F"The male suspect arrived by taxi, he
OL,12,Fpunched the victim, and then left in
OL,13,Fthe taxi. This was at approximately
OL,14,F9pm.
OL,16,F"Carl was taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment to a serious head injury,
OL,18,Fwhere he remained in a critical
OL,19,Fcondition until his untimely death."
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@dO]
