OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781873290
OL,3,CMan dies in hospital week after attack
OL,5,F"You can contact officers on 101 or
OL,6,Freport online at psni.police.uk/
OL,7,Fmakeareport, quoting reference number
OL,8,F1174 13/06/26."
OL,10,FA 20-year-old man previously arrested
OL,11,Fon suspicion of grievous bodily harm
OL,12,Fwith intent was subsequently released
OL,13,Fon bail to allow for further inquiries.
OL,15,FA 46-year-old man and a 44-year-old
OL,16,Fwoman previously arrested on suspicion
OL,17,Fof conspiracy to commit grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm were also bailed as
OL,19,Finquiries continued.
OL,26,@mD@AOUpD@OO]
