OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781873290
OL,3,CMan dies in hospital week after attack
OL,5,FWest Belfast MP Paul Maskey said the
OL,6,Fdeath was "absolutely devastating".
OL,8,FHe said: "I want Carl's loved ones to
OL,9,Fknow that the community stands with
OL,10,Fthem as they endure an extremely
OL,11,Fdifficult period of grief and
OL,12,Fheartbreak.
OL,14,F"Anyone with any information should
OL,15,Fimmediately come forward and contact
OL,16,Fthe PSNI to assist with its
OL,17,Finvestigation."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
